* Tax refund service: Pay 70-1800% to get a tax refund advance loan
* Remittances: Paying to send money to other countries
* Cars: Pay $50-500 more for the exact same car
* Car loans: Pay ~2 pp more on car loans
* Car insurance: Pay $50-1000 more on car insurance
* Home loans: Pay 1pp more on home loans
* Home insurance: Pay $300 more on home insurance
* Durables: Often pay for rent-to-own instead of just buying the item. A $200 TV costs $700 at a rent to own after interest

